| HistoryText             = The Tunnelers were caught in the [[Alley]] when the [[Marauders (Earth-616)|Marauders]] began the [[Mutant Massacre]]. They were one of the few groups of [[Morlocks (Earth-616)|Morlocks]] to defeat the Marauders on their own, losing half their number in repelling the Marauders.

The remaining members ([[Blow-Hard (Earth-616)|Blow-Hard]], [[Masque (Earth-616)|Masque]], [[Scaleface (Earth-616)|Scaleface]], and [[Ray Carter (Earth-616)|Berzerker]]) reluctantly accepted [[X-Factor (Earth-616)|X-Factor]]'s offer of shelter, but later snuck out into the city. While contemplating their future, they were attacked by the [[Savage Wolf Gang (Earth-616)|Savage Wolf Gang]], and later [[New York City Police Department|NYPD police officers]]. X-Factor tried to stop the fighting, but failed, and all but Masque were slain.
